{"id": "33546", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33546", "title": "Vorsha the Lasher (quest)", "text": "This is an escort quest in which the player must protect &lt;a href=\"Muglash\"&gt;Muglash&lt;/a&gt; as he draws out and defeats &lt;a href=\"Vorsha%20the%20Lasher\"&gt;Vorsha the Lasher&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"hydra\"&gt;hydra&lt;/a&gt;.\nObjectives.\nDefeat Vorsha the Lasher.\nDescription.\nVorsha the Lasher... the fiendish hydra that roams the seas...\nShe has attacked our &lt;a href=\"Zoram%27gar%20Outpost\"&gt;outpost&lt;/a&gt;, each time unprovoked, laying waste to anything that falls in her path.\nBut I am ready, &lt;name&gt;. I have prepared to best the hydra and end these attacks on Zoram'gar.\nThe &lt;a href=\"naga\"&gt;naga&lt;/a&gt; honor the wicked nature of this beast with a brazier that remains lit on an island just off the coast. I believe that if we put it out, Vorsha will appear in anger.\nWe will need help, so be sure to bring some strong allies.\nCompletion.\nI have witnessed many naga attacks since I arrived here. It puts my mind at ease that Vorsha will no longer roam freely.\nWe are in your debt, &lt;name&gt;.\nNotes.\nMuglash will set off as soon as the quest is accepted, so be prepared to escort him.\nMuglash will help you out in this fight. Two or three waves of &lt;a href=\"naga\"&gt;naga&lt;/a&gt;, and finally Vorsha itself, will spawn and must be killed. If Muglash dies, the quest will fail."}
