ow Remulos to the &lt;a href=\"Circle%20of%20Spirits\"&gt;Circle of Spirits&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt's time to choose your first &lt;a href=\"artifact\"&gt;artifact&lt;/a&gt;!"}
