{"id": "306652", "revid": "48774054", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=306652", "title": "Tol Barad Peninsula", "text": "Tol Barad Peninsula is the northernmost region of the island of &lt;a href=\"Tol%20Barad\"&gt;Tol Barad&lt;/a&gt; and is a major daily quest hub in \"\".\nQuests.\nTol Barad Peninsula contains two daily quest hubs, one for each faction. The &lt;a href=\"Baradin%27s%20Wardens\"&gt;Baradin's Wardens&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Hellscream%27s%20Reach\"&gt;Hellscream's Reach&lt;/a&gt; each offer a random selection of available daily quests from &lt;a href=\"Baradin%20Base%20Camp\"&gt;Baradin Base Camp&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Hellscream%27s%20Grasp\"&gt;Hellscream's Grasp&lt;/a&gt; for their respective factions. Completion of the quests will generate reputation gains and reward &lt;a href=\"Tol%20Barad%20Commendation\"&gt;Tol Barad Commendation&lt;/a&gt;s which are used to purchase PvP-oriented rewards from faction quartermasters. There are a total of twenty-four daily quests available, of which a random selection will be available each day.\nQuests in this peninsula are unaffected by the world-PvP event which takes place in the adjacent zone &lt;a href=\"Tol%20Barad\"&gt;Tol Barad&lt;/a&gt;. It should be noted that completing the world-PvP event will open up more daily quest opportunities in the zone there.\nResources.\nHerbalism\nMining\nFishing"}
