{"id": "548054", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=548054", "title": "Tol Dagor (instance)", "text": "Tol Dagor is a dungeon in \"\". It is a &lt;a href=\"prison\"&gt;prison&lt;/a&gt; located in an island east of &lt;a href=\"Tiragarde%20Sound\"&gt;Tiragarde Sound&lt;/a&gt;. Tol Dagor used to be a real prison, but some time ago the &lt;a href=\"Ashvane%20Trading%20Company\"&gt;Ashvane Trading Company&lt;/a&gt; bought it. Now it is &lt;a href=\"Priscilla%20Ashvane\"&gt;Priscilla Ashvane&lt;/a&gt;'s own personal fortress with scumbags on both sides of the bars.\nAdventure Guide.\n\"Once a highly maintained prison, Tol Dagor has since been purchased and run by the &lt;a href=\"Ashvane%20Company\"&gt;Ashvane Company&lt;/a&gt;. Now, it serves as indefinite holding for any who would oppose the Ashvane Trading Company.\"\nNarrative.\n&lt;a href=\"Taelia\"&gt;Taelia&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Proudmoore%20Elite\"&gt;Proudmoore Elite&lt;/a&gt;s, and &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s arrive upon the shores of Tol Dagor via boat. They make their way to the first boss at the entrance of the sewers, and defeat the &lt;a href=\"krolusk\"&gt;krolusk&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe party then approaches Tol Dagor's sewer entrance.\nUpon entering &lt;a href=\"Drain%20%28Tol%20Dagor%29\"&gt;The Drain&lt;/a&gt;, a conversation between Ashvane and Korgus is heard.\nMaking their way further through the &lt;a href=\"Sodden%20Depths\"&gt;Sodden Depths&lt;/a&gt;, the conversation continues.\nThey arrive in the &lt;a href=\"Detention%20Block\"&gt;Detention Block&lt;/a&gt;, which Jes Howlis has taken control of, with &lt;a href=\"Irontide%20Raider\"&gt;Irontide Raider&lt;/a&gt;s brutalizing prisoners.\nAfter Howlis' death, a jailer bars the way.\nThe jailer is killed.\nA spotter gives the alarm, and the &lt;a href=\"Ashvane%20Officer\"&gt;Ashvane Officer&lt;/a&gt; and his men bar the way.\nThe officer is killed.\nReaching the surface at the &lt;a href=\"Overseer%27s%20Redoubt\"&gt;Overseer's Redoubt&lt;/a&gt;, the Ashvane are everywhere and try to stop the party's progression. They make a last stand right before Valyri's room. \nThe party reaches the &lt;a href=\"Ashvane%20Armory\"&gt;Ashvane Armory&lt;/a&gt; where they defeat Valyri.\nThey then make their way to the &lt;a href=\"Overseer%27s%20Summit\"&gt;Overseer's Summit&lt;/a&gt;, where they kill Korgus."}
