{"id": "194121", "revid": "46586549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=194121", "title": "Sindragosa's Fall", "text": "Sindragosa's Fall is the &lt;a href=\"boneyard\"&gt;boneyard&lt;/a&gt; where the &lt;a href=\"Lich%20King\"&gt;Lich King&lt;/a&gt; raised &lt;a href=\"Sindragosa\"&gt;Sindragosa&lt;/a&gt;, the frost-queen, as seen in the \"\" cinematic trailer (which can be found &lt;a href=\"http%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D3SGHMTBG3tQ\"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;).\nDuring the &lt;a href=\"War%20of%20the%20Ancients\"&gt;War of the Ancients&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"blue%20dragonflight\"&gt;blue dragonflight&lt;/a&gt; was decimated; and many of the &lt;a href=\"dragon\"&gt;dragon&lt;/a&gt;s fell to ground that later became covered by the &lt;a href=\"Icecrown%20Glacier\"&gt;Icecrown Glacier&lt;/a&gt;. Among them, &lt;a href=\"Malygos\"&gt;Malygos&lt;/a&gt;'s consort &lt;a href=\"Sindragosa\"&gt;Sindragosa&lt;/a&gt; died here as she desperately sought to reach the &lt;a href=\"Dragonblight\"&gt;Dragonblight&lt;/a&gt; \u2014 the place where dragons instinctively travel to die.\nThousands of years later, &lt;a href=\"Arthas%20Menethil\"&gt;Arthas Menethil&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Lich%20King\"&gt;Lich King&lt;/a&gt;, awoke from his long dormancy and journeyed to Sindragosa's Fall, where he raised Sindragosa into undeath as a mighty skeletal &lt;a href=\"frost%20wyrm\"&gt;frost wyrm&lt;/a&gt; and ordered her to lead the &lt;a href=\"Frostbrood\"&gt;Frostbrood&lt;/a&gt; into war. The Lich King tore the spirits of Sindragosa's lost &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20whelp\"&gt;whelps&lt;/a&gt; into undeath in front of her skeletal form as a final affront to the great dragon.\nDuring the &lt;a href=\"war%20against%20the%20Lich%20King\"&gt;war against the Lich King&lt;/a&gt;, the area was crawling with &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Cult of the Damned&lt;/a&gt; acolytes and members who were raising more &lt;a href=\"frost%20wyrm\"&gt;frost wyrm&lt;/a&gt;s from the ice. The quests here involved the &lt;a href=\"Frostbrood\"&gt;Frostbrood&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s were either sent by &lt;a href=\"Thassarian\"&gt;Thassarian&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Koltira%20Deathweaver\"&gt;Koltira Deathweaver&lt;/a&gt; to eliminate the cultist presence there. They later encountered &lt;a href=\"Matthias%20Lehner\"&gt;Matthias Lehner&lt;/a&gt; who offered them a vision of the Lich King raising Sindragosa in return for &lt;a href=\"Whelp%20Bone%20Dust\"&gt;Whelp Bone Dust&lt;/a&gt;s."}
