{"id": "663754", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=663754", "title": "Voidstalker", "text": "Voidstalkers are &lt;a href=\"warp%20stalker\"&gt;warp stalker&lt;/a&gt;s that have been corrupted by the &lt;a href=\"Void\"&gt;Void&lt;/a&gt;, giving them a distinctive purple appearance. They can be found in the Void-corrupted areas of &lt;a href=\"Eredath\"&gt;Eredath&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Argus\"&gt;Argus&lt;/a&gt; and on the world of &lt;a href=\"Telogrus%20Rift\"&gt;Telogrus Rift&lt;/a&gt;. Some &lt;a href=\"Shadowguard\"&gt;Shadowguard&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"void%20ethereal\"&gt;ethereals&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"void%20elf\"&gt;void elf&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Elven%20ranger\"&gt;rangers&lt;/a&gt; use them as pets.\nAs a companion pet.\n&lt;a href=\"Voidstalker%20Runt\"&gt;Voidstalker Runt&lt;/a&gt;s can be captured in pet battles in &lt;a href=\"Eredath\"&gt;Eredath&lt;/a&gt;.\nAs a hunter pet.\nVoidstalkers are tamable by &lt;a href=\"hunter\"&gt;hunter&lt;/a&gt;s as part of the &lt;a href=\"warp%20stalker\"&gt;warp stalker&lt;/a&gt; family. Note that the &lt;a href=\"Voidstalker%20%28Eredath%29\"&gt;Voidstalkers&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enthralled%20Voidstalker\"&gt;Enthralled Voidstalker&lt;/a&gt;s in Eredath are classed as &lt;a href=\"aberration\"&gt;aberration&lt;/a&gt;s and are therefore untamable.\n&lt;a href=\"Void%20elf%20%28playable%29\"&gt;Void elf&lt;/a&gt; hunters start with a voidstalker pet. Hunters from other races were unable to tame voidstalkers until the release of &lt;a href=\"patch%208.3.0\"&gt;patch 8.3.0&lt;/a&gt;."}
