{"id": "81809", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=81809", "title": "Voidwalkers Gone Wild", "text": "Objective.\nBring 10 Condensed Voidwalker Essences to &lt;a href=\"%22Screaming%22%20Screed%20Luckheed\"&gt;\"Screaming\" Screed Luckheed&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Zeppelin%20Crash\"&gt;Zeppelin Crash&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nEven if I can get the &lt;a href=\"zeppelin\"&gt;zeppelin&lt;/a&gt;'s frame repaired, I'll have to find something else to power the engine. I'm all out of fuel and there's no place to fill up around here!\nTo the south of us is an area of broken land called the &lt;a href=\"Warp%20Fields\"&gt;Warp Fields&lt;/a&gt;. It's full of rogue and uncontrolled &lt;a href=\"voidwalker\"&gt;voidwalker&lt;/a&gt;s, but I like to think of them as walking batteries.\nIf you can bring me enough of their essence, I can convert the zeppelin's engine to run on it. Five gold says I'll even get better mileage out of it, too!\nRewards.\nYou will also receive:\nProgress.\nWere you able to get the essence?\nCompleted.\nThis is perfect! In fact, I think it's going to work so well, I might just have to redesign the engine to take advantage of all this extra power. If, I mean, when we get out of here, I'll have to show my design to everyone back at &lt;a href=\"Area%2052\"&gt;Area 52&lt;/a&gt;!\nNotes.\nThe voidwalkers are in the &lt;a href=\"Warp%20Fields\"&gt;Warp Fields&lt;/a&gt;. To get to the fields travel South from the &lt;a href=\"Zeppelin%20Crash\"&gt;Zeppelin Crash&lt;/a&gt; site. If you need a point of reference its directly west of the &lt;a href=\"Expedition%20Armory\"&gt;Expedition Armory&lt;/a&gt;. The voidwalkers are pretty easy to kill even at level 60. The drop rate is about 40% so this is an easy start up quest. The drop rate has been known to be bugged, but just go back a little later and try it again.\nYou might want want to pick up &lt;a href=\"Unyielding%20Souls\"&gt;Unyielding Souls&lt;/a&gt; (from &lt;a href=\"Honor%20Guard%20Wesilow\"&gt;Honor Guard Wesilow&lt;/a&gt; outside short tower from &lt;a href=\"Honor%20Hold\"&gt;Honor Hold&lt;/a&gt;: 51, 60), since the mobs for those quests are nearby at the Expedition Armory.\nThe name of the quest could be a reference to the \"Girls Gone Wild\" adult video line."}
