{"id": "43281", "revid": "40372170", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43281", "title": "Voll", "text": "Voll is one of the &lt;a href=\"jungle%20troll\"&gt;jungle troll&lt;/a&gt; companions (along with &lt;a href=\"Snee\"&gt;Snee&lt;/a&gt;) of &lt;a href=\"Harkyn%20Grymstone\"&gt;Harkyn Grymstone&lt;/a&gt;. Voll is known to be \"always starving\" and he can be recognized by his long tongue, flapping around outside his mouth.\nHistory.\nThe Sunwell Trilogy.\nHe was hired by &lt;a href=\"Dar%27Khan%20Drathir\"&gt;Dar'Khan Drathir&lt;/a&gt; to hunt &lt;a href=\"Kalecgos\"&gt;Kalecgos&lt;/a&gt;.\nDragonflight.\nHe can be found with his companions south-west of &lt;a href=\"Uktulut%20Pier\"&gt;Uktulut Pier&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Waking%20Shores\"&gt;Waking Shores&lt;/a&gt;."}
